Taken from https://etherpad.mozilla.org/foss-event-site
-------------------------------------------------------
1. An API to create/read/update/delete events.
        REST API is prefereable.
        End points:
            /events/<id>:
                method: POST
                request with all the data (name, date, description, tags etc)
                Creates/updates the event
            
                method: GET
                returns json data with event details
                
                method: DELETE
                delete the event.

2. The form requests the API with the data

